{{Infobox_BitLifeApp|title1=Royalty Update - V1.41|launched_on_ios:=September 7, 2020|launched_on_android:=April 19, 2021|image1=File: Better royal update pic.jpg}}

Following the '''Royalty Update in September 2020''', players can now become royalty! (Note: this feature is only available when playing as a character in [[Belgium|Belgium,]] [[Denmark|Denmark,]] [[Japan|Japan,]]  [[Jordan|Jordan,]] [[Kuwait|Kuwait,]] [[Malaysia|Malaysia,]] [[Monaco|Monaco,]] [[Morocco|Morocco,]] [[Netherlands|Netherlands,]] [[Norway|Norway,]] [[Qatar|Qatar,]] [[Saudi Arabia|Saudi Arabia,]] [[Spain|Spain,]] [[Sweden|Sweden,]] [[Thailand|Thailand,]] [[United Arab Emirates|UAE,]] or [[United Kingdom|UK]].) They may be born into different tiers of royal families, or simply marry their way into one! When finally royal, characters can command whoever they'd like be executed, laws be passed or ignored, celebrities be invited into their royal homes, and more... And on top of that, manage a whole new "Respect" stat— closely tied to the already-existing [[Stats/Fame|"Fame"]] stat.

